{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1325c0bc00","title":"应奉行大的战略击破敌之要害","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9aba1d9f66","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":15,"articleId":"1325c0bc00"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"82ea8647cb","type":"paragraph","text":"应奉行大的战略击破敌之要害”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00"},{"id":"c3efdd1318","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月15日）彭、任：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00"},{"id":"d1e26fc892","type":"paragraph","text":"无论军事政治方面，目前均须击破敌之要害。敌之要害不是宁夏或甘肃，而是河南与南京。敌已奉行大规模内战，我们对战争是后发，不是先发。然在敌主力向西安进时，我军应奉行大的战略，迁回并击破敌头脑之南京政府。此方针应无疑义。行动务求萌蔽，一切人不得下达。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00"},{"id":"944c484e5e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00"},{"id":"5ca4be5604","type":"paragraph","text":"十五日二十时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00"},{"id":"4e4b71d550","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东在西安事变后为应付国民党可能发动的大规模内战，关于红军大的战略给红军前敌总指挥彭德怀和政治委员任弱时的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00"}],"page":{"id":"7e7527cb9f","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"1325c0bc00","start":168,"end":168}}}},"__N_SSG":true}